name: Stephen Ferrell
text: This was my first time ordering from here. I placed an order online and was given a 40-50 minute wait. According to the website I would receive both a text message and an email when my order was finished. After 45 minutes I walked in after â€¦More

name: Jason Thomas
text: Very good pizza. A little bit different than most, which is a welcome change when you've pretty much tasted them all. Very glad you came to Delavan so we could have the pleasure of ordering your pizza.  Will definitely continue ordering from you!

name: Don Miller
text: Lightning fast service, pizza tasted great and delivered piping hot!  Used the website to place order - an excellent way to custom order your pizza!  Finally a pizza restaurant in Delavan that knows what a "thin crust" pizza is!  Don Miller, Lake Geneva

name: Carmelo Alfano
text: friends ordered their pizza.  expensive for a franchise and not that great.  Better local options in the area.
